CHRISTIANA TRUST, a Division of Wilmington Savings Fund Society, FSB, et al., Plaintiffs,
v.
Joseph LIBERATI, et al., Defendants. (Patricia Liberati - Petitioner) (U.S. Bank National Association - Respondent) C-102 September Term 2018
081178 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005588-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
